ce (SQUID) amplifiers. Up to 78 bolometers will be multiplexed with a\nsingle SQUID amplidier.\n  We report on the sub-Kelvin instrument design and ongoing developments for\nthe LiteBIRD mission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 08:25:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Jan 2018 21:34:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 15 Mar 2018 20:07:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-13"}
