 temperature dependence\nof resistance from 4 K to 300 K ruling out any hoping mediated or activated\nelectrical transport.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 11:28:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-22"}
